Mourners will first gather at the University of Johannesburg&#8217;s Soweto campus before the late actor is laid to rest at the Westpark Cemetery. JOHANNESBURG - Veteran actor Joe Mafela will also be laid to rest at the Westpark Cemetery on Wednesday morning.Mafela died in a car crash on the M1 in Johannesburg earlier this month. He was 75.Mourners will first gather at the University of Johannesburg s Soweto campus before the late actor is laid to rest at the Westpark Cemetery.WATCH: Joe Mafela is laid to rest